    {
      "type": "para:s1",
      "text": "The Preaching of John the Baptist"
    },
    {
      "type": "para:r",
      "text": "(Matthew 3.1-12; Luke 3.1-18; John 1.19-28)"
    },
    {
      "type": "para:p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "verse:v",
          "number": "1",
          "sid": "JHN 1:1"
        },
        "This is the Good News about Jesus Christ, the Son of God. ",
        {
          "type": "verse:v",
          "number": "2",
          "sid": "JHN 1:2"
        },
        "It began as the prophet Isaiah had written:"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para:q1",
      "vid": "JHN 1:2",
      "text": "\u201cGod said, \u2018I will send my messenger ahead of you"
    },
    {
      "type": "para:q2",
      "vid": "JHN 1:2",
      "children": [
        "to open the way for you.\u2019"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para:q1",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "verse:v",
          "number": "3",
          "sid": "JHN 1:3"
        },
        "Someone is shouting in the desert,"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para:q2",
      "vid": "JHN 1:3",
      "text": "\u2018Get the road ready for the Lord;"
    },
    {
      "type": "para:q2",
      "vid": "JHN 1:3",
      "children": [
        "make a straight path for him to travel!\u2019\u201d"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para:p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "verse:v",
          "number": "4",
          "sid": "JHN 1:4"
        },
        "So John appeared in the desert, baptizing and preaching. \u201cTurn away from your sins and be baptized,\u201d he told the people, \u201cand God will forgive your sins.\u201d"
      ]
    }
  ]
}